      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: Pact of the Blade feature</em><br />Your pact weapon alters how certain weapon properties work when wielded by you.</p><ul><li>While wielding a weapon with the versatile property in one hand you can roll the weapon's damage as if you were wielding it with two hands.</li><li>Thrown attacks at long range does not impose disadvantage on your ranged weapon attack rolls, and the weapon can repair in your hand as part of the same attack.</li><li>You ignore the loading property of the weapon.</li><li>You do not reduce the damage die of a weapon that has it's damage die reduces as a result of the special property.</li></ul>",
